∀ {u v : ℝ},
  0 < u → u < Real.sqrt 2 → 0 < v →
    IsMin (fun p : ℝ × ℝ => (p.1 - v) ^ 2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - p.1 ^ 2) - 9 / p.2) ^ 2) (u, v)

∀ {u v : ℝ}, 0 < u → u < Real.sqrt 2 → 0 < v → 
  ∃ min_val, is_minimum (λ u v, (u - v)^2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - u^2) - (9 / v))^2) min_val

∀ {u v : ℝ}, 0 < u ∧ u < Real.sqrt 2 ∧ 0 < v → 
  (u - v) ^ 2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - u ^ 2) - 9 / v) ^ 2 ≥ some_minimum_value

∀ {u v : ℝ}, 0 < u → u < Real.sqrt 2 → 0 < v → 
  ∃ (min_val : ℝ), min_val = (u - v)^2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - u^2) - 9 / v)^2

∀ {u v : ℝ}, 0 < u ∧ u < Real.sqrt 2 ∧ 0 < v → 
  (∃ m, ∀ u' v', 0 < u' ∧ u' < Real.sqrt 2 ∧ 0 < v' → (u' - v')^2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - u'^2) - 9 / v')^2 ≥ m)

∀ {u v : ℝ}, 0 < u → u < Real.sqrt 2 → 0 < v →
  (u - v) ^ 2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - u ^ 2) - 9 / v) ^ 2 ≥ 8

∀ {u v : ℝ}, 0 < u ∧ u < Real.sqrt 2 ∧ 0 < v → 
  ∃ (x y : ℝ), x = u ∧ y = v ∧ 
    (x - u) ^ 2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - x ^ 2) - 9 / y) ^ 2 = (u - v) ^ 2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - u ^ 2) - 9 / v) ^ 2

∀ {u v : ℝ}, 0 < u → u < Real.sqrt 2 → 0 < v → 
  ∃ (x : ℝ), x = ((u - v) ^ 2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - u ^ 2) - 9 / v) ^ 2) ∧ ∀ y, y < x
∀ {u v : ℝ}, 0 < u ∧ u < Real.sqrt 2 → 0 < v → ∃ w, w = (u - v) ^ 2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - u ^ 2) - 9 / v) ^ 2 → w = 1

∀ {u v : ℝ}, 0 < u ∧ u < Real.sqrt 2 ∧ 0 < v → 
  (∀ x y, 0 < x ∧ x < Real.sqrt 2 ∧ 0 < y → (x - v)^2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - x^2) - 9 / y)^2 ≥ (u - v)^2 + (Real.sqrt (2 - u^2) - 9 / v)^2)
